'''Fuchsia'''是[[Google|Google]]开发的[[操作系统|操作系统]]<ref name="businessinsider"><cite class="citation web">Prince, Rob. </cite></ref>，與基于[[Linux内核|Linux内核]]的[[Chrome_OS|Chrome OS]]和[[Android|Android]]等不同，Fuchsia基于新的名为Zircon的[[微内核|微内核]]<ref name="tnw"><cite class="citation web">Lopez, Napier (13 August 2016). </cite></ref>，受Little Kernel启发<ref name="github_src">{{cite web|title=magenta/mg_and_lk.md at 1e009f296dc397a2a0ba3a9fe364a662a57a3ace · fuchsia-mirror/magenta |url = https://github.com/fuchsia-mirror/magenta/blob/1e009f296dc397a2a0ba3a9fe364a662a57a3ace/docs/mg_and_lk.md |website=GitHub|access-date=26 Oct 2016}}{{Dead link |date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>，用于嵌入式系统，主要使用[[C语言|C语言]]和C++编写<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.tomshardware.com/news/google-fuchsia-new-operating-system,32475.html "Google Is Building A New Operating System From Scratch: 'Fuschia'"]. 2016-08-15<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>。Fuchsia的设计目标之一是可运行在众多的设备上，包括[[移动电话|移动电话]]和[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]。<ref name="engadget"><cite class="citation web">Fingas, Jon. </cite></ref>

[[File:Google_Fuchsia_Logo.svg|thumb]]

作为免费和[[开源软件|开源软件]]分发，采用[[BSD许可证|三句版BSD]]，[[MIT許可證|MIT]]和[[Apache_2.0|Apache 2.0]]软件许可证。

== 历史 ==
2016年8月，媒体报道了发布于[[GitHub|GitHub]]上的神秘[[源码|源码]]，显示Google正在开发一个名为“Fuchsia”的新操作系统，虽然官方没有正式公布，其源码检查显示其能够[[跨平台|跨平台]]运行，包括“汽车的娱乐媒体系统和嵌入式设备，如[[红绿灯|红绿灯]]、[[数码手表|数码手表]]、[[智能手机|智能手机]]、[[平板电脑|平板电脑]]与[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]”。<ref>{{cite web |first=Darrell |last=Etherington |title=Google’s mysterious new Fuchsia operating system could run on almost anything |url=https://techcrunch.com/2016/08/15/googles-mysterious-new-fuchsia-operating-system-could-run-on-almost-anything/ |website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=August 15, 2016 |accessdate=October 5, 2016 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605085438/https://techcrunch.com/2016/08/15/googles-mysterious-new-fuchsia-operating-system-could-run-on-almost-anything/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Jon |last=Fingas |title=Google's Fuchsia operating system runs on virtually anything |url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/08/13/google-fuchsia-operating-system/ |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=August 13, 2016 |accessdate=October 5, 2016 |archive-date=2019-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190210073256/https://www.engadget.com/2016/08/13/google-fuchsia-operating-system/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

2017年5月，Ars Technica编写了关于Fuchsia的新[[用户界面|用户界面]]的文章，从8月首次披露时的命令行界面上升级，以及开发人员表示“此项目不是玩具项目，不是20%时间项目，不是我们不再关心的死去的项目的垃圾场”，多家媒体写到“Fuchsia项目”和[[Android|Android]]似乎有密切联系，有人猜测Fuchsia可能是“重做”<ref>{{cite web |first=Jon |last=Fingas |title=Google's mysterious Fuchsia OS looks like an Android re-do |url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/08/google-fuchsia-os-matures/ |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=May 8, 2017 |accessdate=May 9, 2017 |archive-date=2019-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211060715/https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/08/google-fuchsia-os-matures/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>或替换Android<ref>{{cite web |first=Chaim |last=Gartenberg |title=Google’s mysterious new Fuchsia OS has a UI now |url=https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2017/5/8/15579846/google-fuchsia-os-magenta-armadillo-first-look-ui |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=May 8, 2017 |accessdate=May 9, 2017 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605141656/https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2017/5/8/15579846/google-fuchsia-os-magenta-armadillo-first-look-ui |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Corbin |last=Davenport |title=Google's "Fuchsia" operating system is taking shape with a new design |url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/05/08/googles-fuchsia-operating-system-taking-shape-new-design/ |website=Android Police |date=May 8, 2017 |accessdate=May 9, 2017 |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031184359/https://www.androidpolice.com/2017/05/08/googles-fuchsia-operating-system-taking-shape-new-design/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以在某种程度上修复该平台上的问题。

2017年11月，对[[Swift_(程式語言)|Swift]]语言提供了初始支持。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/apple/swift/pull/12955|title=Add Fuchsia OS support|work=GitHub PR for Swift|date=2017-11-15|accessdate=2018-02-02|archive-date=2019-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501101434/https://github.com/apple/swift/pull/12955|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年1月3日，Google允许开发者以Google Pixelbook为目标设备，下载Fuchsia OS进行开发与测试<ref>[https://github.com/fuchsia-mirror/docs/blob/master/hardware/pixelbook.md Preparing to install Fuchsia on Pixelbook]{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}.GitHub.[2018-01-03].</ref><ref>[https://github.com/fuchsia-mirror/docs/blob/master/fuchsia_paver.md#paving Putting Fuchsia on a Device]{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}.GitHub.[2018-01-03].</ref><ref>[http://technews.cn/2018/01/03/google-is-now-testing-its-mysterious-fuchsia-os-on-the-pixelbook/ Google允许以自家Pixelbook测试Fuchsia OS] {{Wayback|url=http://technews.cn/2018/01/03/google-is-now-testing-its-mysterious-fuchsia-os-on-the-pixelbook/ |date=20180129141337 }}.科技新報.[2018-01-03].</ref>。

2018年4月，Fuchsia的原始碼出現在[[AOSP|AOSP]]的[[ART|ART]]當中，疑似是AOSP已經開始將ART移植至Fuchsia上，但原始碼仍處於被註釋處理的狀態。<ref>{{cite web|title=谷歌 Fuchsia 源码现身 AOSP，支持 ART 运行环境 - 开源中国社区|url=https://www.oschina.net/news/95595/google-fuchsia-source-code-in-aosp|website=www.oschina.net|language=zh-CN|accessdate=2018-05-11|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609142140/https://www.oschina.net/news/95595/google-fuchsia-source-code-in-aosp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年6月28日，Fuchsia OS的开发者网站Fuchsia.dev上线。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fuchsia.dev: Google launches official site about Fuchsia OS|url=https://9to5google.com/2019/06/28/google-launches-fuchsia-dev/|accessdate=2019-06-29|date=2019-06-28|last=Bradshaw|first=Kyle|work=9to5Google|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120010052/https://9to5google.com/2019/06/28/google-launches-fuchsia-dev/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年12月8日，首度在Google Open Source 部落格亮相，籲開發者來做出貢獻。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Expanding Fuchsia's open source model|url=https://opensource.googleblog.com/2020/12/expanding-fuchsias-open-source-model.html|date=2020-12-08|language=en-US|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115165557/https://opensource.googleblog.com/2020/12/expanding-fuchsias-open-source-model.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 特性 ==
Fuchsia的[[用户界面|用户界面]]与[[移动应用程序|应用]]使用“[[Flutter_(软件)|Flutter]]”开发。Flutter是一个能为Fuchsia、[[Android|Android]]和[[iOS|iOS]]进行跨平台开发的开发框架，基于[[Dart|Dart]]创建应用，能让应用达到120[[帧率|FPS]]的高性能。

得益于Flutter提供的跨平台能力，用户可以在Android设备上安装一部分Fuchsia。[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]注意到尽管用户可以测试Fuchsia，但是并不“可用”。他们还补充，尽管能看出Fuchsia与Android的界面有很多相似之处，比如应用屏幕、设置彩蛋和同时浏览多个应用的分屏功能等，但“全都只是占据位置而不可用”<ref name="ars-fuchsia">{{cite web |first=Ron |last=Amadeo |title=Google’s “Fuchsia” smartphone OS dumps Linux, has a wild new UI |url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/05/googles-fuchsia-smartphone-os-dumps-linux-has-a-wild-new-ui/ |website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] |date=2017-05-08 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2019-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926205306/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/05/googles-fuchsia-smartphone-os-dumps-linux-has-a-wild-new-ui/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Ars Technica注意到Fuchsia的很多部分都能工作，尤其是硬件支持<ref name="ars-fuchsia2">{{cite web|first=Ron|last=Amadeo|title=Google’s Fuchsia OS on the Pixelbook: It works! It actually works!|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2018/01/googles-fuchsia-os-on-the-pixelbook-it-works-it-actually-works/|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|date=2018-01-08|accessdate=2018-04-04|quote=Right now, Google's built-from-scratch kernel and operating system will actually boot on the Pixelbook, and some things even work. The touchscreen, trackpad, and keyboard work and so do the USB ports. You can even plug in a mouse and get a second mouse cursor.|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217001841/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2018/01/googles-fuchsia-os-on-the-pixelbook-it-works-it-actually-works/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

